Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:05.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Go to Ibuki-sensei's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:06.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll meet her in person and ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:12.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then we'll know for sure\Nif she's Ibuki-sensei's sister or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'll come with us, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.85,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko will wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why? We'll get things done faster if you meet her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:01:59.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why doesn't she want to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,There might be a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How can we believe her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:10.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We don't know if she's a ghost or a wandering phantom,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:14.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,but it's ridiculous to think that\Nshe's a spirit and her body's at a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's human no matter how you look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:19.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Well that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:22.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:25.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe like a reason that forces her to say she's Ibuki Fuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:30.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Or maybe she believes she's Ibuki Fuuko for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What kind of reason could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:38.65,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:38.65,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}A Scene with a Sculpture
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:41.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good evening. I'm Furukawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.70,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan. How unexpected of you to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:48.59,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:51.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, you're the person that came to buy bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:55.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, you know Ibuki-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:59.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I gave her Sanae-san's bread once\Nwhen there wasn't anyone in your store.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:02.15,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,So is he your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:04.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Ah, I didn't mean that I don't like you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:11.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um… I'm sure there's a person better suited for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:14.62,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Do you already have someone you're in a relationship with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, I don't have anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.06,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Looks like you have a good chance, Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,P-Please pretend you didn't hear what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.59,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan's cute, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, ah….
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:36.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Right! Sensei! Congratulations on getting engaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:42.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I heard that there's a certain Yuusuke-san that you'll be marrying soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:45.38,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So we're here to congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.49,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Who did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:51.50,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,His name, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:56.18,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,I didn't tell this to anyone but my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:04:00.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're sure? You've only told your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.71,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Yes, to my sister who's in a deep, long sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:09.44,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan. You know how\Nmy sister, Fuuko, is sleeping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:10.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:15.37,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Even though she's asleep, I talk to her often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:17.83,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,I've told her about my marriage, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.49,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,But no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We heard a rumor about it at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:27.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe someone who saw you walking\Nwith your boyfriend embellished the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.71,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,I see. Then that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,How is your sister doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:37.10,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,I went to check up on her a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:40.97,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Her complexion looked better than other days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:49.24,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm not sure if I'll get married or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:52.56,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,Given the situation my sister is in,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:58.65,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,I can't make the decision if I should get married and just have my own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:06.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:08.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I almost couldn't stop myself from telling her…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…that Fuuko-chan is at school right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Everything's solved by having the two of them meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:21.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But I feel this is something\NI shouldn't talk about so carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:23.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Fuuko-chan was against it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:27.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa, do you really believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:30.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That she's a ghost or spirit or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:38.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If it's about the marriage,\Nmaybe she overheard the guy talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:43.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I know it is strange, but I don't think Fuuko-chan is lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:54.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Fuuko-chan is making those sculptures to get people to celebrate her sister's marriage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I won't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Instead…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Help her with what she's trying to accomplish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:10.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You get really worked up if it's for others, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about the drama club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:17.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's also important, but I can't leave\NFuuko-chan alone in a state like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:22.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I know you've helped me a lot, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:27.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fuuko's situation does bother me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I've got nothing better to do, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.43,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Are you sure Fuuko can impose upon you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:47.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I can't let you sleep at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:53.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your parents know of Ibuki-sensei, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, since she comes often to buy bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then we should hide her last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come up with something, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.28,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.19,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.49,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,you want us to let her stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:09.50,San,San,0,0,0,,We have no problem with it, but what about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, they're horrible parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They left her behind and went away on a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:15.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.34,San,San,0,0,0,,What's your last name, Fuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.51,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's Isogai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She sure picked a unique one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.42,San,San,0,0,0,,Isogai Fuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.35,San,San,0,0,0,,Isogai-san is our neighbor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:34.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:40.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She took the next-door neighbor's last name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Is she the neighbor's relative or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not at all! It's a complete coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:47.58,San,San,0,0,0,,I see. So it's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:52.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think we could have fooled them even if we had said, “Ibuki”.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:53.83,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.95,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko will be in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.38,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, she knows her manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.84,San,San,0,0,0,,We look forward to getting to know you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.01,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.51,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I won't be so forgiving if it happens again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.52,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.49,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,They went to peep on the girl's dormitory again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:24.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They want your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:28.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Be a little more strict and I bet they'll stop being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.23,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Is it something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A slap isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:37.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think a joint lock would be enough against them even with a woman's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:40.09,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I don't like violence, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:42.50,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Oh, Okazaki. You're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, peeping tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.22,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:44.84,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Hold him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:48.13,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Divine punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,My arm hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:55.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Now I can't go mess with the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Regarding the drama club,\Nwe won't be doing anything for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We have something else to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:01.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Something else to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:04.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. Babysitting a ghost girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not that I believe she's a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:07.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Huh? Ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:11.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fuuko bothers me, but I'm worried about Furukawa, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:14.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So I'll be helping out and keeping an eye on them for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Therefore, give me tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.50,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That doesn't follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.94,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.17,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I'm bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you doing so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.81,San,San,0,0,0,,Good morning, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Have you all been carving these since last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:56.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, we're helping Fuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.61,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, you have a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:09:59.82,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:00.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:00.88,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's not something you should be asking your daughter's friend to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:05.21,San,San,0,0,0,,He's right, Akio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:08.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's right, Sanae-san. Tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.85,San,San,0,0,0,,We can carve these while minding the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:15.94,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If Sanae says she loves me that much, then fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No one said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.22,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,All right, time for labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:19.79,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll get ready for school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:31.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When you see all of them together, the floor looks like a starry sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.99,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, these are stars, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.92,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,No, they're starfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:41.45,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,They're starfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:46.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You were making starfish the entire time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:50.09,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Of course. Fuuko doesn't understand why Fuuko would have to carve stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.11,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,That doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Starfish make even less sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:57.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Seeing them all together makes them very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:10:59.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Starfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:02.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did she tell you these were starfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, that's what I thought they were from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:08.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How can you tell?\NAnd do you think starfish are cute, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:11.28,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They are, since Fuuko-chan made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:20.72,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:23.61,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We managed to give out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.99,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,We can give out a lot thanks to you two helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:36.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you rather meet\Nyour sister than be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:43.63,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko does want to meet her,\Nbut Fuuko wonders if she'll hear Fuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:44.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:50.53,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko thinks Fuuko is here doing this\Nbecause Fuuko can't see or talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.06,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Because there isn't anything else Fuuko can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:58.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, Fuuko-chan. What does your sister call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.34,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then can I call you that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:03.46,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can I call you that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.05,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,That'd be horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:06.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.37,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It just is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:08.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Miyazawa, you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.34,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.94,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,And this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:21.39,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Um, please take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:21.96,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.71,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,A present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.56,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:35.75,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I see. So she's doing this to get students to celebrate her sister's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. And we're cheering her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.74,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'll be cheering you on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.98,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.98,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You take everything in stride, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It was nice to have her accept it, wasn't it, Fuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:54.09,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Yes. It was thanks to you, Nagisa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:54.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.29,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Because you're Fuuko's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.05,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Then Fuuko's nemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:58.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's gotten worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.25,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It'd be better to say you're Fuuko's archnemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You can't pick on Fuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So she enters that state when Nagisa hugs her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, Fuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Calling her name is useless.\NShe's gone for a while once she's in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fujibayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.24,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:18.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Can you come here for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:24.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When she comes back to us, tell her,\N”I'm Okazaki; I just turned into a girl.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:28.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's always spacing out,\Nso I want to give her a little warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will you help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.32,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Sure, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:35.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If she asks what happened, tell her, “{\i1}It{\i0\fscx50} {\r} falls off every now and then.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:38.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,For anything else, just say, “I guess.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:39.17,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll hide and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:47.13,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is this really for Fuu-chan's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:51.14,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Um, what were we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.09,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Eh? Where did Okazaki-san and Nagisa-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:57.87,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm Okazaki; I just turned into a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:01.81,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I said, I'm Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.23,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I just turned into a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.33,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,This doesn't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:09.15,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Why did you turn into a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:11.76,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-It{\i0\fscx50} {\r} falls off every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.84,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,That's too big of a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:17.53,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,So it… falls off every now and then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Gosh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:18.62,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I-I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:22.33,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You guess?! It falls off that easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:25.09,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko never knew such a person existed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:29.53,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Looking at it in reverse, is there\Na chance of one attaching to Fuuko, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.34,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.34,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It could happen?! Fuuko is utterly shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.67,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It reattached?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:36.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:39.91,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,So it was a bad dream, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:44.29,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. Fuuko thought Fuuko might one day become Fuutaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:44.29,Note,Fuk,0,0,0,,Note: “Taro” is a typically masculine ending for a name
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:47.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, you should tell her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.90,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,There are two Okazaki-sans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:51.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We split into two on occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.66,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko is utterly shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.26,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:59.24,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I've been watching! Stop playing pranks using my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.18,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Same face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:05.20,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,There are three Okazaki-sans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How much longer can she do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:13.99,Note,Oka,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)}“Switch the Person She's Talking To” Mastered!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:14.80,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:16.17,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're giving these to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.99,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.56,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Or maybe it's a starfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:23.55,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You're wonderful! You're part of Fuuko's starfish alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.66,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What? This really is a starfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:29.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. A sculpture of starfish Fuuko made with all her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:33.78,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Umm… I meant it as a joke, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.69,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Give the starfish a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.54,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.11,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,You look wonderful! It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.11,0:15:42.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What kind of tastes does she have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:46.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But they're both beautiful,\Nso seeing them lined up makes them look very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Inside, they're completely different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The older one is a gorilla and the younger is a hamster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:55.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.94,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You just said something really rude, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:01.04,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,You can't throw something you received.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:04.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah! If you do that, Fuuko will be—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:11.51,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry. It looked like it had\Na good damage bonus, so I moved without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:14.17,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Flying starfish…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.10,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Everyone is accepting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:25.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, we are picking out kind people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.40,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Mitsui-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.99,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It's Ibuki Fuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.25,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,We talked a little during the entrance ceremony, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.09,Default,Mit,0,0,0,,Yes, I recall that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.96,Default,Mit,0,0,0,,You got into an accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.13,Default,Mit,0,0,0,,Were you released from the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.71,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:42.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She got released and is starting over as a freshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And we have a little favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.56,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Please accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:48.81,Default,Mit,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.48,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,A present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:55.93,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,And if possible, Fuuko hopes you can come to Fuuko's sister's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.68,Default,Mit,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:06.57,Default,Mit,0,0,0,,You're a freshman, so you might not understand,\Nbut seniors are at an important time with entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:10.44,Default,Mit,0,0,0,,I don't want to do anything that leads to a loss of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.19,Default,Mit,0,0,0,,Excuse me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Fuu-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:23.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you cheer up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.45,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko is doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm saying so because you don't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:32.00,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko only got to talk to Mitsui-san\Na little during the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:35.24,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,It was good enough that she remembered Fuuko's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:38.24,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko hasn't attended any classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:44.48,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko is only picking up extra wood\Nand carving in open classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:50.71,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko wanted to attend classes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right then. Time to call Kyou and Sunohara then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:02.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It looks lively even though it's the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, since the Founders Festival's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They must be getting ready for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:07.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, we can enter the campus, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.60,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Ah, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:15.04,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Good morning, Okazaki-san,\NFurukawa-san, and Fuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:17.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:19.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry to have you all come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:22.47,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I came for Nagisa-chan, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Sunohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:28.08,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,But Tomoya, why do we have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There are a few reasons behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:31.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll explain all of them some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.84,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Fuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.09,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko is a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Come here, Fuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Class will be starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.39,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Get over here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:57.44,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,We have the students,\Nbut what are we doing about the teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:02.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I couldn't ask a real teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:05.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then is one of us doing the teacher role?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not you, since you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.94,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.58,San,San,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.08,San,San,0,0,0,,Class is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.23,San,San,0,0,0,,I heard the story from Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.71,San,San,0,0,0,,If you're okay with it, allow me to fill the teacher's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:24.00,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, Tomoya, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.43,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Nagisa's older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.08,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hot chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Looks like this'll be a fun class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We have one person\Nin a different world from the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.90,San,San,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone, please take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:43.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san looks really comfortable with the teacher role.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:47.16,San,San,0,0,0,,Since this is the first class, I'd like everyone to introduce themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:47.83,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.10,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm Sunohara Youhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.21,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,The kanji for Sunohara is spring-field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.83,San,San,0,0,0,,My, that's a beautiful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.94,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Sensei, Sunohara-kun is an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't go saying things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:19:59.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She would have found out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.13,San,San,0,0,0,,Sunohara-kun, make up for it with your energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm Okazaki Tomoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:08.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm a lazy bum at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.19,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes, it's nice to handle things at your own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm Furukawa Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:18.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san and Okazaki-san are goofing off,\Nbut I want to take the class seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:21.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I guess that makes you the class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.64,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.86,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You should become the class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.03,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Rather than me…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:32.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I recommend Fuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:35.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since this class is centered around Fuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fuuko! Are you up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:45.36,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,No objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.80,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Good luck with the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:50.08,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If that's what Nagisa-chan says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:55.47,San,San,0,0,0,,So, class representative. Please introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:56.29,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Ibuki-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.78,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Isogai Fuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.37,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko likes starfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.33,San,San,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:05.88,San,San,0,0,0,,Fuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:16.19,San,San,0,0,0,,Fuuko-chan, everyone you see\Naround you is your classmate…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.70,San,San,0,0,0,,…and is your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:35.64,San,San,0,0,0,,Let's all get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:37.12,Default,All,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:40.06,San,San,0,0,0,,Let's start the class now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.34,San,San,0,0,0,,Class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:44.07,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You have to say the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:44.91,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:46.07,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:47.73,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.73,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:57.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ibuki Fuuko…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:05.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's a little strange, but she's a normal girl\Nno matter how you look at her.
