Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:43.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ask Ibuki-sensei to come to the Founders Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:49.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm thinking of inviting her to the festival and letting the two of them meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:51.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see. That might be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.57,0:23:50.27,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:54.88,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Um, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:23:56.67,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Please have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.67,0:24:01.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to let Fuu-chan and Ibuki-sensei meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:05.60,Ibu,Ibu,0,0,0,,We promised to go to\Nthe Founders Festival when she enrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:08.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, Fuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.37,0:24:09.02,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Yes!
